name: Large Whipped Body Butter
description:
Aay Jays Oasis Whipped Butters are infused with vitamins A, E and F and all natural ingredients that regenerate skin cells, increase skin wall flexibility, soothe, hydrate and revitalize damaged skin and hair. All Whipped butters are made from all natural ingredients. These Whipped Butters will have your skin nourished, glowing, feeling new and silky smooth!

Ingredients of Scented: Butyrospermum Parkii(Shea Butter), Oleic Acid, Stearic Acid, Palmitic  Acid, Linoleic Acid, Olive Oil and Fragrance

Ingredients of Unscented:Butyrospermum Parkii(Shea Butter), Oleic Acid, Stearic Acid, Palmitic  Acid, Linoleic Acid and Olive Oil


**Local Deliveries Available in NYC. Please send order through Contact link***
